opencard.core.util

Interface TraceLevels

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TracerEvent

    public interface TraceLevels
    Constants used by Tracer. The tracing levels were modeled on the Linux syslog() facility.
    Version:
    $Id: TraceLevels.java,v 1.1.1.1 1999/10/05 15:34:32 damke Exp $
    Author:
